{"title":"Potion of confusion/zh-CN","url":"https://nethackwiki.com/wiki/Potion_of_confusion/zh-CN","type":"markdown","data":"**NetHack 中文 Wiki 需要您的帮助！**  \n[了解如何帮助我们完善Wiki](/wiki/NetHackWiki:How_to_help/zh-CN \"NetHackWiki:How to help/zh-CN\")\n\n**[English](/wiki/Potion_of_confusion \"Potion of confusion\")**\n\n • [한국어](/wiki/Potion_of_confusion/ko \"Potion of confusion/ko\")\n\n • [中文（中国大陆）‎]()\n\n| ! [![Pink potion.png](/images/7/79/Pink_potion.png)](/wiki/File:Pink_potion.png) |                                                                                                                              |\n| -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |\n| 名称                                                                               | 混乱                                                                                                                           |\n| 外观                                                                               | [随机](/index.php?title=%E9%9A%8F%E6%9C%BA%E5%A4%96%E8%A7%82\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"随机外观 (page does not exist)\")             |\n| 基础价                                                                              | 100 [zm](/wiki/%E9%87%91%E5%B8%81 \"金币\")                                                                                      |\n| 重量                                                                               | 20                                                                                                                           |\n| 怪物使用                                                                             | *怪物会将其用作[攻击物品](/index.php?title=%E6%94%BB%E5%87%BB%E7%89%A9%E5%93%81\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"攻击物品 (page does not exist)\")。* |\n\n**混乱药水**（potion of confusion）是[NetHack](/index.php?title=NetHack/zh-CN\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"NetHack/zh-CN (page does not exist)\")中的一种[药水](/wiki/%E8%8D%AF%E6%B0%B4 \"药水\")。\n\n[ ]\n\n## Contents\n\n- [1 生成](#.E7.94.9F.E6.88.90)\n- [2 描述](#.E6.8F.8F.E8.BF.B0)\n- [3 策略](#.E7.AD.96.E7.95.A5)\n- [4 历史](#.E5.8E.86.E5.8F.B2)\n- [5 消息](#.E6.B6.88.E6.81.AF)\n- [6 Variants](#Variants)\n  - [6.1 SLASH'EM](#SLASH.27EM)\n- [7 引用及注释](#.E5.BC.95.E7.94.A8.E5.8F.8A.E6.B3.A8.E9.87.8A)\n\n## 生成\n\n有[智能](/index.php?title=%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"智能 (page does not exist)\")的怪物生成时可能会获得用作[攻击物品](/index.php?title=%E6%94%BB%E5%87%BB%E7%89%A9%E5%93%81\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"攻击物品 (page does not exist)\")的混乱药水[\\[1\\]](#cite_note-1)。\n\n将[酒](/wiki/%E9%85%92 \"酒\")与[启蒙药水](/wiki/%E5%90%AF%E8%92%99%E8%8D%AF%E6%B0%B4 \"启蒙药水\")[混合](/index.php?title=%E6%B5%B8\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"浸 (page does not exist)\")可以[调制](/index.php?title=%E7%82%BC%E9%87%91%E6%9C%AF\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"炼金术 (page does not exist)\")出混乱药水。\n\n## 描述\n\n如名称所述，[饮用](/index.php?title=%E9%A5%AE%E7%94%A8\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"饮用 (page does not exist)\")该药水会让你获得数[回合](/index.php?title=%E5%9B%9E%E5%90%88\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"回合 (page does not exist)\")的[混乱](/index.php?title=%E6%B7%B7%E4%B9%B1\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"混乱 (page does not exist)\")效果。混乱的持续时间依药水的[BUC](/index.php?title=BUC/zh-CN\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"BUC/zh-CN (page does not exist)\")而定[\\[2\\]](#cite_note-2)：\n\n- 祝福：8～14回合\n- 未诅咒：16～22回合\n- 诅咒：24～30回合\n\n将[独角兽的角](/wiki/%E7%8B%AC%E8%A7%92%E5%85%BD%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%92 \"独角兽的角\")浸入混乱药水会将其转化为未诅咒的[水](/wiki/%E6%B0%B4%EF%BC%88%E8%8D%AF%E6%B0%B4%EF%BC%89 \"水（药水）\")。将混乱药水与[获得能量药水](/wiki/%E8%8E%B7%E5%BE%97%E8%83%BD%E9%87%8F%E8%8D%AF%E6%B0%B4 \"获得能量药水\")或[升级药水](/index.php?title=%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7%E8%8D%AF%E6%B0%B4\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"升级药水 (page does not exist)\")混合会调制出[酒](/wiki/%E9%85%92 \"酒\")或[启蒙药水](/wiki/%E5%90%AF%E8%92%99%E8%8D%AF%E6%B0%B4 \"启蒙药水\")。\n\n怪物会以混乱药水攻击玩家，击中时也会造成混乱。吸入混乱药水的[蒸汽](/index.php?title=%E8%92%B8%E6%B1%BD\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"蒸汽 (page does not exist)\")会导致玩家进入1～5回合的混乱状态[\\[3\\]](#cite_note-3)。被混乱药水击中的怪物也会进入混乱状态，该效果可能被[怪物魔抗](/index.php?title=%E6%80%AA%E7%89%A9%E9%AD%94%E6%8A%97\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"怪物魔抗 (page does not exist)\")抵御[\\[4\\]](#cite_note-4)。\n\n## 策略\n\n混乱药水可以用于主动进入混乱状态，来发挥[部分卷轴的特殊效果](/index.php?title=%E6%B7%B7%E4%B9%B1\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"混乱 (page does not exist)\")，不过，游戏中也有其他占背包容量更少的混乱来源。因此，混乱药水更适合用来攻击怪物、[批量变形](/index.php?title=%E6%89%B9%E9%87%8F%E5%8F%98%E5%BD%A2\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"批量变形 (page does not exist)\")或[稀释](/wiki/%E7%A8%80%E9%87%8A \"稀释\")成水。\n\n## 历史\n\n混乱药水最初于[Jay Fenlason's Hack](/wiki/Jay_Fenlason%27s_Hack \"Jay Fenlason's Hack\")的衍生作品Hack 1.21和Hack for PDP-11里出现，也是[Hack 1.0](/wiki/Hack_1.0 \"Hack 1.0\")中最初加入游戏的物品之一。\n\n## 消息\n\n- 哈？什么？我在哪儿？（Huh, What? Where am I?）\n\n  你喝下了混乱药水。\n\n- 好一个古怪的幻觉！（What a trippy feeling!）\n\n  同上，但你处于[幻觉](/index.php?title=%E5%B9%BB%E8%A7%89\\&action=edit\\&redlink=1 \"幻觉 (page does not exist)\")状态。\n\n- 你感到有些头晕。（You feel somewhat dizzy.）\n\n  你被投掷出的混乱药水击中了。\n\n## Variants\n\n**此条目或段落的部分内容需要翻译。**  \n您可以帮助我们[**翻译此页面**](https://nethackwiki.com/index.php?title=Potion_of_confusion/zh-CN\\&action=edit)，但**请勿使用机器翻译**。\n\n### SLASH'EM\n\nIn [SLASH'EM](/wiki/SLASH%27EM \"SLASH'EM\"), the [Lawful Quest](/wiki/Lawful_Quest \"Lawful Quest\") has a 2⁄5 chance of generating a cursed potion of confusion among the items found in the Chamber of Junk.\n\n## 引用及注释\n\n1. [↑](#cite_ref-1) [src/makemon.c in NetHack 3.6.7, line 556](https://github.com/NetHack/NetHack/blob/NetHack-3.6.7_Released/src/makemon.c#L556)\n2. [↑](#cite_ref-2) [src/potion.c in NetHack 3.6.7, line 902](https://github.com/NetHack/NetHack/blob/NetHack-3.6.7_Released/src/potion.c#L902)\n3. [↑](#cite_ref-3) [src/potion.c in NetHack 3.6.7, line 1700](https://github.com/NetHack/NetHack/blob/NetHack-3.6.7_Released/src/potion.c#L1700)\n4. [↑](#cite_ref-4) [src/potion.c in NetHack 3.6.7, line 1466](https://github.com/NetHack/NetHack/blob/NetHack-3.6.7_Released/src/potion.c#L1466)\n\n[![此条目的内容已同步至NetHack 3.6.7。详细信息请点击此处。](/images/f/f7/Nh367-icon.png)](/wiki/NetHackWiki:Next_version \"此条目的内容已同步至NetHack 3.6.7。详细信息请点击此处。\")\n","html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html class=\"client-nojs\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\"/>\n<title>Potion of confusion/zh-CN - NetHack Wiki</title>\n<script>document.documentElement.className = document.documentElement.className.replace( /(^|\\s)client-nojs(\\s|$)/, \"$1client-js$2\" );</script>\n<script>(window.RLQ=window.RLQ||[]).push(function(){mw.config.set({\"wgCanonicalNamespace\":\"\",\"wgCanonicalSpecialPageName\":false,\"wgNamespaceNumber\":0,\"wgPageName\":\"Potion_of_confusion/zh-CN\",\"wgTitle\":\"Potion of confusion/zh-CN\",\"wgCurRevisionId\":176536,\"wgRevisionId\":176536,\"wgArticleId\":40962,\"wgIsArticle\":true,\"wgIsRedirect\":false,\"wgAction\":\"view\",\"wgUserName\":null,\"wgUserGroups\":[\"*\"],\"wgCategories\":[\"Offensive items/zh-CN\",\"待翻译页面\",\"Nethack-367 articles\",\"Potions/zh-CN\"],\"wgBreakFrames\":false,\"wgPageContentLanguage\":\"en\",\"wgPageContentModel\":\"wikitext\",\"wgSeparatorTransformTable\":[\"\",\"\"],\"wgDigitTransformTable\":[\"\",\"\"],\"wgDefaultDateFormat\":\"dmy\",\"wgMonthNames\":[\"\",\"January\",\"February\",\"March\",\"April\",\"May\",\"June\",\"July\",\"August\",\"September\",\"October\",\"November\",\"December\"],\"wgMonthNamesShort\":[\"\",\"Jan\",\"Feb\",\"Mar\",\"Apr\",\"May\",\"Jun\",\"Jul\",\"Aug\",\"Sep\",\"Oct\",\"Nov\",\"Dec\"],\"wgRelevantPageName\":\"Potion_of_confusion/zh-CN\",\"wgRelevantArticleId\":40962,\"wgRequestId\":\"0164e7114ac09f27a88292b6\",\"wgCSPNonce\":false,\"wgIsProbablyEditable\":false,\"wgRelevantPageIsProbablyEditable\":false,\"wgRestrictionEdit\":[],\"wgRestrictionMove\":[],\"wgWikiEditorEnabledModules\":[],\"wgCategoryTreePageCategoryOptions\":\"{\\\"mode\\\":0,\\\"hideprefix\\\":20,\\\"showcount\\\":true,\\\"namespaces\\\":false}\"});mw.loader.state({\"site.styles\":\"ready\",\"noscript\":\"read