<a href=\"/wiki/File:Pink_potion.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Pink potion.png\" src=\"/images/7/79/Pink_potion.png\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>名称\n</th>\n<td>混乱\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>外观\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%9A%8F%E6%9C%BA%E5%A4%96%E8%A7%82&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"随机外观 (page does not exist)\">随机</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>基础价\n</th>\n<td>100 <a href=\"/wiki/%E9%87%91%E5%B8%81\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"金币\">zm</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>重量\n</th>\n<td>20\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>怪物使用\n</th>\n<td><small><i>怪物会将其用作<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E6%94%BB%E5%87%BB%E7%89%A9%E5%93%81&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"攻击物品 (page does not exist)\">攻击物品</a>。</i></small>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n</div>\n<p><b>混乱药水</b>（potion of confusion）是<a href=\"/index.php?title=NetHack/zh-CN&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"NetHack/zh-CN (page does not exist)\">NetHack</a>中的一种<a href=\"/wiki/%E8%8D%AF%E6%B0%B4\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"药水\">药水</a>。\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#.E7.94.9F.E6.88.90\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">生成</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#.E6.8F.8F.E8.BF.B0\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">描述</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#.E7.AD.96.E7.95.A5\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">策略</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#.E5.8E.86.E5.8F.B2\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">历史</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#.E6.B6.88.E6.81.AF\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">消息</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Variants\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Variants</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#SLASH.27EM\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">SLASH'EM</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#.E5.BC.95.E7.94.A8.E5.8F.8A.E6.B3.A8.E9.87.8A\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">引用及注释</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span id=\"生成\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E7.94.9F.E6.88.90\">生成</span></h2>\n<p>有<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"智能 (page does not exist)\">智能</a>的怪物生成时可能会获得用作<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E6%94%BB%E5%87%BB%E7%89%A9%E5%93%81&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"攻击物品 (page does not exist)\">攻击物品</a>的混乱药水<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>。\n</p><p>将<a href=\"/wiki/%E9%85%92\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"酒\">酒</a>与<a href=\"/wiki/%E5%90%AF%E8%92%99%E8%8D%AF%E6%B0%B4\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"启蒙药水\">启蒙药水</a><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E6%B5%B8&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"浸 (page does not exist)\">混合</a>可以<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E7%82%BC%E9%87%91%E6%9C%AF&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"炼金术 (page does not exist)\">调制</a>出混乱药水。\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"描述\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E6.8F.8F.E8.BF.B0\">描述</span></h2>\n<p>如名称所述，<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%A5%AE%E7%94%A8&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"饮用 (page does not exist)\">饮用</a>该药水会让你获得数<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%9B%9E%E5%90%88&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"回合 (page does not exist)\">回合</a>的<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E6%B7%B7%E4%B9%B1&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"混乱 (page does not exist)\">混乱</a>效果。混乱的持续时间依药水的<a href=\"/index.php?title=BUC/zh-CN&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"BUC/zh-CN (page does not exist)\">BUC</a>而定<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>：\n</p>\n<ul><li>祝福：8&#xff5e;14回合</li>\n<li>未诅咒：16&#xff5e;22回合</li>\n<li>诅咒：24&#xff5e;30回合</li></ul>\n<p>将<a href=\"/wiki/%E7%8B%AC%E8%A7%92%E5%85%BD%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%92\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"独角兽的角\">独角兽的角</a>浸入混乱药水会将其转化为未诅咒的<a href=\"/wiki/%E6%B0%B4%EF%BC%88%E8%8D%AF%E6%B0%B4%EF%BC%89\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"水（药水）\">水</a>。将混乱药水与<a href=\"/wiki/%E8%8E%B7%E5%BE%97%E8%83%BD%E9%87%8F%E8%8D%AF%E6%B0%B4\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"获得能量药水\">获得能量药水</a>或<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7%E8%8D%AF%E6%B0%B4&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"升级药水 (page does not exist)\">升级药水</a>混合会调制出<a href=\"/wiki/%E9%85%92\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"酒\">酒</a>或<a href=\"/wiki/%E5%90%AF%E8%92%99%E8%8D%AF%E6%B0%B4\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"启蒙药水\">启蒙药水</a>。\n</p><p>怪物会以混乱药水攻击玩家，击中时也会造成混乱。吸入混乱药水的<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E8%92%B8%E6%B1%BD&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"蒸汽 (page does not exist)\">蒸汽</a>会导致玩家进入1&#xff5e;5回合的混乱状态<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>。被混乱药水击中的怪物也会进入混乱状态，该效果可能被<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E6%80%AA%E7%89%A9%E9%AD%94%E6%8A%97&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"怪物魔抗 (page does not exist)\">怪物魔抗</a>抵御<sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>。\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"策略\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E7.AD.96.E7.95.A5\">策略</span></h2>\n<p>混乱药水可以用于主动进入混乱状态，来发挥<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E6%B7%B7%E4%B9%B1&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"混乱 (page does not exist)\">部分卷轴的特殊效果</a>，不过，游戏中也有其他占背包容量更少的混乱来源。因此，混乱药水更适合用来攻击怪物、<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E6%89%B9%E9%87%8F%E5%8F%98%E5%BD%A2&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"批量变形 (page does not exist)\">批量变形</a>或<a href=\"/wiki/%E7%A8%80%E9%87%8A\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"稀释\">稀释</a>成水。\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"历史\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E5.8E.86.E5.8F.B2\">历史</span></h2>\n<p>混乱药水最初于<a href=\"/wiki/Jay_Fenlason%27s_Hack\" title=\"Jay Fenlason&#39;s Hack\">Jay Fenlason's Hack</a>的衍生作品Hack 1.21和Hack for PDP-11里出现，也是<a href=\"/wiki/Hack_1.0\" title=\"Hack 1.0\">Hack 1.0</a>中最初加入游戏的物品之一。\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"消息\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E6.B6.88.E6.81.AF\">消息</span></h2>\n<dl><dt><span id=\".E5.93.88.EF.BC.9F.E4.BB.80.E4.B9.88.EF.BC.9F.E6.88.91.E5.9C.A8.E5.93.AA.E5.84.BF.EF.BC.9F\">哈？什么？我在哪儿？</span>（Huh, What?  Where am I?）</dt>\n<dd>你喝下了混乱药水。</dd>\n<dt><span id=\".E5.A5.BD.E4.B8.80.E4.B8.AA.E5.8F.A4.E6.80.AA.E7.9A.84.E5.B9.BB.E8.A7.89.EF.BC.81\">好一个古怪的幻觉！</span>（What a trippy feeling!）</dt>\n<dd>同上，但你处于<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%B9%BB%E8%A7%89&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"幻觉 (page does not exist)\">幻觉</a>状态。</dd>\n<dt><span id=\".E4.BD.A0.E6.84.9F.E5.88.B0.E6.9C.89.E4.BA.9B.E5.A4.B4.E6.99.95.E3.80.82\">你感到有些头晕。</span>（You feel somewhat dizzy.）</dt>\n<dd>你被投掷出的混乱药水击中了。</dd></dl>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Variants\">Variants</span></h2>\n<div class=\"todo\">\n<p><b>此条目或段落的部分内容需要翻译。</b><br />\n您可以帮助我们<a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://nethackwiki.com/index.php?title=Potion_of_confusion/zh-CN&amp;action=edit\"><b>翻译此页面</b></a>，但<b>请勿使用机器翻译</b>。\n</p>\n</div>\n<h3><span id=\"SLASH'EM\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"SLASH.27EM\">SLASH'EM</span></h3>\n<p>In <a href=\"/wiki/SLASH%27EM\" title=\"SLASH&#39;EM\">SLASH'EM</a>, the <a href=\"/wiki/Lawful_Quest\" title=\"Lawful Quest\">Lawful Quest</a> has a <sup>2</sup>&#8260;<sub>5</sub> chance of generating a cursed potion of confusion among the items found in the Chamber of Junk.\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"引用及注释\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E5.BC.95.E7.94.A8.E5.8F.8A.E6.B3.A8.E9.87.8A\">引用及注释</span></h2>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/NetHack/NetHack/blob/NetHack-3.6.7_Released/src/makemon.c#L556\">src/makemon.c in NetHack 3.6.7, line 556</a>\n     </span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/NetHack/NetHack/blob/NetHack-3.6.7_Released/src/potion.c#L902\">src/potion.c in NetHack 3.6.7, line 902</a>\n     </span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/NetHack/NetHack/blob/NetHack-3.6.7_Released/src/potion.c#L1700\">src/potion.c in NetHack 3.6.7, line 1700</a>\n     </span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/NetHack/NetHack/blob/NetHack-3.6.7_Released/src/potion.c#L1466\">src/potion.c in NetHack 3.6.7, line 1466</a>\n     </span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<div style=\"display:none; right:10px; padding-bottom: 17px\" class=\"metadata topicon nopopups\"><div style=\"margin-top: -10px\"><a href=\"/wiki/NetHackWiki:Next_version\" title=\"此条目的内容已同步至NetHack 3.6.7。详细信息请点击此处。\"><img alt=\"此条目的内容已同步至NetHack 3.6.7。详细信息请点击此处。\" src=\"/images/f/f7/Nh367-icon.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20240926185731\nCache expiry: 604800\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.049 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.095 seconds\nPre